parameters:
Dining Hall Chef: We received quite a troublesome
ingredient. Would you mind helping me with the cooking?
Dining Hall Chef: Unfortunately... I feel discouraged.

Dining Hall Chef: Really!? Please come before you change
your mind!

Dining Hall Chef: I managed to finish cooking somehow!
Please accept this as my gratitude!

Dining Hall Chef: You understand the troublesome reason,
right...?

Miner Man: Having a decent cook is the only enjoyment we
have when it comes to meals.

Dining Hall Lady: Food is important for physical work! It's
my job to satisfy hungry men.

Female cafeteria staff: There are few women here, so hehe, I
get approached every day and it's tough.

Miner Man: Don't worry, it's okay! Wine is strictly
prohibited except after work.

Miner Man: A new employee, huh!? Unlike weak men, I'm tough,
you know?

Miner Man: There was a guy who stole the crystal... I try
not to think about what happened to him.
